a lot lately.

56:47.246 --> 56:50.350
Why are you here?

56:50.484 --> 56:53.819
Well, I died
alone, apparently.

56:53.953 --> 56:56.522
Why did you die alone?

56:56.656 --> 57:00.159
I was picky, really picky.

57:00.293 --> 57:04.131
Yeah, I was single a lot.

57:04.264 --> 57:05.798
Weren't you lonely?

57:05.931 --> 57:09.235
I was.
Yes, I was lonely.

57:09.369 --> 57:11.804
And why are you still alone?

57:11.938 --> 57:13.440
You know, I could ask you
the same question.

57:13.574 --> 57:16.109
Well, you could, but I'm not
the one who's dead.

57:18.545 --> 57:20.147
But you are alone.
I mean...

57:20.279 --> 57:22.248
Why are you alone today,
for instance?

57:22.382 --> 57:24.884
