you would have never met me.

57:37.498 --> 57:39.566
True.

57:39.699 --> 57:41.701
Wow.
You can see me.

57:41.835 --> 57:44.638
Okay, what else do you see?

57:44.770 --> 57:47.640
I see you, and I see

57:47.775 --> 57:51.811
shifty little flickers
of people

57:51.944 --> 57:53.980
