58:36.522 --> 58:37.956
I love baseball.
You?

58:38.090 --> 58:42.061
- Of course not.
- That figures.

58:44.663 --> 58:46.532
You're good at this.

58:46.665 --> 58:48.133
So, I guess
we're not soul mates,

58:48.268 --> 58:50.570
